  "text": "We studied 39 patients (age ranging from 20-45 years; mean age, 33.35 6 8.4 years) from 20 families with a molecularly confirmed diagnosis of LHON, harboring either the 11778/ ND4, 3460/ND1, or 14484/ND6 mutation. Each pedigree also was assessed for the mtDNA haplogroup, [CITATION_1] which confirmed that they were unrelated. A total of 22 eyes from 22 normal age-similar subjects (mean age, 38.2 6 6.0 years; range, 19-48 years) served as controls.",
